              <!--<h3>FOGSI Mission</h3>-->
              <p>The main objectives of the Society are - </p>
              <ul>
                  <li>To enhance the knowledge in recent advances in Obstetrics and Gynaecology in the State of Telangana.</li>
                  <li>To promote the improvement of Public Health with special reference to the better care of the expectant mother.</li>
                  <li>To create public awareness for the Holistic development of a girl to a women </li>
                  <li>To promote honorable practice, to repress malpractice and to decide all questions of professional usage or courtesy among the practitioners of Obstetrics and Gynaecology.</li>
                  <li>To maintain the honor and dignity and uphold the interests of the medical profession in general and the practitioners of Obstetrics and Gynaecology in particular.</li>
                  <li>To conduct special programs to Save the Girl Child – to say no to Female Feticide.</li>
                  <li>To conduct programs to Dheera - Stop Violence Against Women (VAW)</li>
                  <li>To conduct Dheera TOT programs to Obgyns</li>
                  <li>To conduct programs on Dheera Online School Certificate Courses</li>
                  <li>To conduct programs to Respectable Abortion Care (RAC) TOT to Obgyns</li>
                  <li>To conduct programs to Naipunya (to encourage training of our Paramedical Staff)</li>
              </ul>
